{"id": "dzn1665702834956", "title": "Defining Popup Forms", "breadcrumbs": ["Developing Desktop Applications", "Forms", "Popup Forms", "Defining Popup Forms"], "url": "https://docs.rocketsoftware.com/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/dzn1665702834956.html", "html": "<html><body><header class=\"zDocsTopicPageHead\"><h1 class=\"css-g931ng\">Defining Popup Forms</h1><div class=\"zDocsTopicActions\" role=\"list\"><div class=\"zDocsBundlePagination\" data-testid=\"next-prev-container\" role=\"listitem\"><div class=\"zDocsPrevTopicButton zDocsPrevTopicButton\"><span class=\"\"><a aria-label=\"Previous:  Popup Forms   \" class=\"\" data-tooltip-content=\"Previous:  Popup Forms   \" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsTopicActionsTooltip\" data-tooltip-open=\"false\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/xzh1665702651987.html\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-prev\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-prev\"></use></svg></a></span></div><div class=\"zDocsNextTopicButton zDocsNextTopicButton\"><span class=\"\"><a aria-label=\"Next:  Defining Single Document Interface (SDI) Behavior  \" class=\"\" data-tooltip-content=\"Next:  Defining Single Document Interface (SDI) Behavior  \" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsTopicActionsTooltip\" data-tooltip-open=\"false\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/tnl1665702834887.html\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-next\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-next\"></use></svg></a></span></div></div><div class=\"zDocsMyDocsMenu\" role=\"listitem\"><span aria-expanded=\"false\" aria-label=\"Add to My Topics\" class=\"d-none d-lg-flex\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" data-tooltip-content=\"Add to My Topics\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsTopicActionsTooltip\" id=\"addToMyDocsDropdownTrigger\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-bookmark-add\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-bookmark-add\"></use></svg></span><span class=\"d-lg-none d-flex\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-bookmark-add\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-bookmark-add\"></use></svg>Add to My Topics</span><div aria-labelledby=\"pdfDropdown\" class=\"dropdown-menu dropdown-menu-right\"><a class=\"zDocsAddTopicButton zDocsMyDocsMenuItem dropdown-item\" href=\"/de-DE/auth/login?redirect=/bundle/uniface_104/page/dzn1665702834956.html?finish_action=mydocs_topic_and_sub\">Add selected topic and subtopics</a><a class=\"zDocsAddTopicButton zDocsMyDocsMenuItem dropdown-item\" href=\"/de-DE/auth/login?redirect=/bundle/uniface_104/page/dzn1665702834956.html?finish_action=mydocs_topic_and_sub_head\">Add Topic &amp; Subtopics with topic head</a><a class=\"zDocsAddTopicButton zDocsMyDocsMenuItem dropdown-item\" href=\"/de-DE/auth/login?redirect=/bundle/uniface_104/page/dzn1665702834956.html?finish_action=mydocs_pub\">Add entire publication</a></div></div><div class=\"zDocsWatchButton\" role=\"listitem\"><span aria-label=\"Watch\" class=\"d-lg-flex d-none zDocsSubscribeButton\" data-tooltip-content=\"Watch\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsTopicActionsTooltip\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-eye\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-eye\"></use></svg></span><span class=\"d-lg-none d-flex zDocsSubscribeButton\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-eye zDocsSubscribeButton\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-eye\"></use></svg><span class=\"zDocsSubscribeButton\">Watch</span></span></div><div class=\"zDocsExportPdfMenu zDocsExportMenu\" data-testid=\"export-pdf-menu\" role=\"listitem\"><span aria-expanded=\"false\" aria-label=\"Download PDF\" class=\"d-none d-lg-flex\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" data-tooltip-content=\"Download PDF\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsTopicActionsTooltip\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-pdf\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-pdf\"></use></svg></span><span class=\"d-lg-none d-flex\" data-return-focus=\"#zDocsTopicActionsMobile\" data-target=\"#ZdExportPDFModal\" data-toggle=\"modal\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-pdf\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-pdf\"></use></svg>Download PDF</span><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu\"><a class=\"zDocsExportItem zDocsExportTopicButton\" href=\"#\" id=\"singlePdf\" role=\"button\">Save selected topic</a><a class=\"zDocsExportItem zDocsExportSubtopicsButton\" href=\"#\" id=\"pdfWithChildren\" role=\"button\">Save selected topic and subtopics</a><a class=\"zDocsExportItem zDocsExportBundleButton\" href=\"#\" id=\"wholeBundlePdf\" role=\"button\">Save entire publication</a></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicShare zDocsShareButton\" role=\"listitem\"><span aria-expanded=\"false\" aria-label=\"Share\" class=\"d-none d-lg-flex zDocsShareDialogButton\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" data-tooltip-content=\"Share\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsTopicActionsTooltip\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-share\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-share\"></use></svg></span><span class=\"d-lg-none zDocsShareDialogButton\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-share\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-share\"></use></svg>Share</span><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu\"><a class=\"dropdown-item zDocsShareButton zDocsShareEmail\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\"><span>Email Link</span></a><a class=\"dropdown-item zDocsShareButton zDocsShareLink\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\"><span>Copy Link</span></a></div></div><div class=\"zDocsFeedback zDocsFeedback zDocsTopicFeedback\" role=\"listitem\"><span aria-label=\"Feedback\" class=\"zDocsFeedbackButton d-none d-lg-flex\" data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_main_2527047\" data-toggle=\"modal\" data-tooltip-content=\"Feedback\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsTopicActionsTooltip\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-feedback\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-feedback\"></use></svg></span><span class=\"d-lg-none d-flex zDocsFeedbackButton\" data-backdrop=\"static\" data-return-focus=\"#zDocsTopicActionsMobile\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_main_2527047\" data-toggle=\"modal\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-feedback\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-feedback\"></use></svg><span class=\"zDocsFeedbackButtonText\"> Feedback</span></span></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><button aria-label=\"Show topic actions\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" id=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-ellipsis-h\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-ellipsis-h\"></use></svg></button><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu zDocsTopicActionsMobileDropdown dropdown-menu-right\"></div></div><div style=\"flex-basis: 100%; height: 0px;\"></div><ul class=\"zDocsTopicPageDetails\"><li class=\"zDocsTopicPageDate css-cinqea\">Last Updated<span class=\"css-cinqea\">Sept 12, 2024</span></li><li class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryDetailsItem\"><button class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryButton\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-topic-summary\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-topic-summary\"></use></svg>Summarize</button></li><li class=\"spacer\" role=\"presentation\"></li><div class=\"zDocsLabelWrapper\"><ul><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: Uniface\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=prod_uniface\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>Uniface</a></li><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: 10.4\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=uniface_10.4\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>10.4</a></li></ul></div></ul></header><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBody\" data-prismjs-copy=\"Copy\" data-prismjs-copy-error=\"Copy failed! Use Ctrl + C instead.\" data-prismjs-copy-success=\"Copied!\"><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBodyContent\" dir=\"ltr\"><div id=\"zDocsAiSummaryContaineruniface_104dzn1665702834956.html\"></div><div><article class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/dzn1665702834956.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/dzn1665702834956.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"dzn1665702834956\" role=\"article\">\n<h1 class=\"title topictitle1\" id=\"ariaid-title1\">\n                     \n Defining Popup Forms \n   </h1>\n<div class=\"body conbody\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">Use the <span class=\"ph uicontrol\">Window Type</span> and other component instance properties to define a popup form.\n </p>\n<section class=\"section context\" id=\"dzn1665702834956__topic_d24686e1_d24687e1_d24688e1\">\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"dzn1665702834956__p_d24689e1_d24690e1_d24691e1\">For more information, see <a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"dto1665702580637.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/dto1665702580637.html\" title=\"Window property of a form that determines the type of window used to display the form. One of: Normal | Dialog | Primary | Secondary | Contained | Popup\">Window Type (WindowType)</a> and <a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"rhe1665702581016.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/rhe1665702581016.html\" title=\"A popup window displays a form in a secondary window that is anchored to a field. The position of the popup window is configurable, so that it can be displayed outside or inside the boundaries of its parent field.\">Popup Window</a>.</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section ul\" id=\"dzn1665702834956__section_w529ab1b5b3_w530ab1b5_w531ab1\">\n<ul class=\"ul\">\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"dzn1665702834956__li_d12293e1_d12294e1_d12295e1\">\n<p class=\"p\">To define a popup form, set the <span class=\"ph uicontrol\">Window Type</span> property to\n                     <code class=\"ph codeph\">Popup</code>. You can do this in the Window Properties of the form,\n                  or in ProcScript when creating the component instance.</p>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"dzn1665702834956__p_d24692e1_d24693e1_d24694e1\">For example, a form with the following code\n                  defines a popup form in the default position. (The <span class=\"ph uicontrol\">Background\n                     Color</span> of the popup form is <code class=\"ph codeph\">Info</code>.)</p>\n<div class=\"code-toolbar\"><pre class=\"pre language-plaintext\" tabindex=\"0\"><code class=\"language-plaintext\">trigger detail; of FLD1\n newinstance \"POPUP_FRM\", \"popup\", \"windowtype=popup\"\n activate \"popup\"\nend</code></pre><div class=\"toolbar\"><div class=\"toolbar-item\"><button class=\"copy-to-clipboard-button\" data-copy-state=\"copy\" type=\"button\"><span>Copy</span></button></div></div></div>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"dzn1665702834956__p_d24695e1_d24696e1_d24697e1\">By default, the popup form is positioned below\n                  the FLD1 field, starting from the bottom left corner.</p>\n<div class=\"p\" id=\"dzn1665702834956__p_d24698e1_d24699e1_d24700e1\">\n<figure class=\"fig fignone\" id=\"dzn1665702834956__fig_w532ab1b5b3b1b1b9b1_w533ab1b5b3b1b1b9_w534ab1b5b3b1b1_w535ab1b5b3b1_w536ab1b5b3_w537ab1b5_w538ab1\">\n<img alt=\"Popup Form in Default position\" class=\"image\" src=\"https://docs-be.rocketsoftware.com/bundle/uniface_104/page/popupformbasic.png?_LANG=enus\"/>\n</figure>\n</div>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"dzn1665702834956__li_d12296e1_d12297e1_d12298e1\">\n<p class=\"p\">To change the position of the popup form, set the Position window property. This\n                  can only be done in ProcScript. </p>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"dzn1665702834956__p_d24701e1_d24702e1_d24703e1\">For example, the following code changes the\n                  anchor point for the popup window to the bottom right corner, and displays to\n                  below and to the left of that corner:</p>\n<div class=\"code-toolbar\"><pre class=\"pre language-plaintext\" tabindex=\"0\"><code class=\"language-plaintext\">trigger detail; of FLD1\n newinstance \"POPUP_FRM\", \"popup\", \"windowtype=popup<span class=\"ph gold\">;</span>position=BOTTOMRIGHT_DOWNLEFT\"\n activate \"popup\"\nend</code></pre><div class=\"toolbar\"><div class=\"toolbar-item\"><button class=\"copy-to-clipboard-button\" data-copy-state=\"copy\" type=\"button\"><span>Copy</span></button></div></div></div>\n<div class=\"p\" id=\"dzn1665702834956__p_d24704e1_d24705e1_d24706e1\">\n<figure class=\"fig fignone\" id=\"dzn1665702834956__fig_w539ab1b5b3b1b3b7b1_w540ab1b5b3b1b3b7_w541ab1b5b3b1b3_w542ab1b5b3b1_w543ab1b5b3_w544ab1b5_w545ab1\">\n<img alt=\"Popup form with position bottomright_downleft\" class=\"image\" src=\"https://docs-be.rocketsoftware.com/bundle/uniface_104/page/popupformposition.png?_LANG=enus\"/>\n</figure>\n</div>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"dzn1665702834956__li_d12299e1_d12300e1_d12301e1\">\n<p class=\"p\">Optionally, set other properties of the popup window using the Properties\n                  Inspector or the <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">newinstance</span> ProcScript statement. </p>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"dzn1665702834956__p_d24707e1_d24708e1_d24709e1\">In the Properties Inspector, click the More icon\n                     (<img alt=\"Click the More icon to open a dialog box\" class=\"image\" id=\"dzn1665702834956__image_oq3_r5v_rcc\" src=\"https://docs-be.rocketsoftware.com/bundle/uniface_104/page/ellipsis.png?_LANG=enus\"/>) of the component's <span class=\"ph uicontrol\">Window Properties</span> to open the\n                  window properties dialog.</p>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"dzn1665702834956__p_d24710e1_d24711e1_d24712e1\">In ProcScript when creating the component\n                  instance.</p>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"dzn1665702834956__p_d24713e1_d24714e1_d24715e1\">In this example, POPUP_NORMAL is a normal form\n                  with the <span class=\"ph uicontrol\">Caption</span> and <span class=\"ph uicontrol\">Close</span>\n                  properties set to <code class=\"ph codeph\">true</code>. When displayed as a popup form, these\n                  properties are ignored by default. However, they are applied when InheritWinProps\n                  is <code class=\"ph codeph\">true</code>.</p>\n<div class=\"code-toolbar\"><pre class=\"pre language-plaintext\" tabindex=\"0\"><code class=\"language-plaintext\">trigger detail; of FLD1\n newinstance \"POPUP_NORMAL\", \"popup\", \"windowtype=popup<span class=\"ph gold\">;</span>InheritWinProps=true<span class=\"ph gold\">;</span>position=BOTTOMRIGHT_UPRIGHT\"\n activate \"popup\"\nend</code></pre><div class=\"toolbar\"><div class=\"toolbar-item\"><button class=\"copy-to-clipboard-button\" data-copy-state=\"copy\" type=\"button\"><span>Copy</span></button></div></div></div>\n<div class=\"p\" id=\"dzn1665702834956__p_d24716e1_d24717e1_d24718e1\">\n<figure class=\"fig fignone\" id=\"dzn1665702834956__fig_w546ab1b5b3b1b5c11b1_w547ab1b5b3b1b5c11_w548ab1b5b3b1b5_w549ab1b5b3b1_w550ab1b5b3_w551ab1b5_w552ab1\">\n<img alt=\"Popup form with inherited properties\" class=\"image\" src=\"https://docs-be.rocketsoftware.com/bundle/uniface_104/page/popupforminheritwinprops.png?_LANG=enus\"/>\n</figure>\n</div>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"dzn1665702834956__p_d24719e1_d24720e1_d24721e1\">For more information, see <a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"bcn1665702597290.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/bcn1665702597290.html\" title=\"Form instance property of a popup form that determines whether the it inherits the window properties that have been explicitly defined for the form. It can be set in ProcScript using newinstance. Valid values: True or False (default).\">InheritWinProps</a> and <a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"rld1665702581999.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/rld1665702581999.html\" title=\"Window property of a form that determines what happens when it loses input focus. It may be automatically closed and the Quit or Accept trigger fired , or it may stay open and be explicitly closed. Valid values: Quit or True, Accept , or False.\">Auto Close (AutoClose)</a>.</p>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"dzn1665702834956__li_d12302e1_d12303e1_d12304e1\">\n<p class=\"p\">To refine the position of the popup form, so that it can be displayed from a\n                  specific point inside or outside the widget. set the PopupRect widget property.\n                  This can only be done in ProcScript using the <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$fieldproperties</span>\n                  function. </p>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"dzn1665702834956__p_d24722e1_d24723e1_d24724e1\">For example, the following code defines a\n                  rectangle of 100 by 10 pixels, starting 4 characters to the right and 1 character\n                  down from the upper left corner of the field.</p>\n<div class=\"code-toolbar\"><pre class=\"pre language-plaintext\" tabindex=\"0\"><code class=\"language-plaintext\">trigger detail; of FLD1\n newinstance \"POPUP_FRM\", \"popup\", \"windowtype=popup\"\n $fieldproperties(FLD1) = \"popuprect=4,1,100px,10px\"\n activate \"popup\"\nend</code></pre><div class=\"toolbar\"><div class=\"toolbar-item\"><button class=\"copy-to-clipboard-button\" data-copy-state=\"copy\" type=\"button\"><span>Copy</span></button></div></div></div>\n<div class=\"p\" id=\"dzn1665702834956__p_d24725e1_d24726e1_d24727e1\">\n<figure class=\"fig fignone\" id=\"dzn1665702834956__fig_w553ab1b5b3b1b7b7b1_w554ab1b5b3b1b7b7_w555ab1b5b3b1b7_w556ab1b5b3b1_w557ab1b5b3_w558ab1b5_w559ab1\">\n<img alt=\"Popup form for popup rectangle\" class=\"image\" src=\"https://docs-be.rocketsoftware.com/bundle/uniface_104/page/popuprect.png?_LANG=enus\"/>\n</figure>\n</div>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</section>\n</div>\n</article></main></article>\n</div></div><div class=\"contentPlaceholder\" style=\"height: 500px;\"><div class=\"contentContainer zDocsSideBoxes\"><div><h5 aria-level=\"5\" class=\"css-g931ng\">Related Links</h5><ul><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/xzh1665702651987.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>Popup Forms</a><p>Popup forms are displayed as secondary windows that are anchored to a field, although their position is completely configurable. They can be used in situations where you want to display or gather a limited amount of data, for example, in a ribbon bar or super tooltip.</p></li></ul></div></div></div></div><div class=\"bottomFeedback\"><div aria-labelledby=\"bottomFeedbackText\" class=\"bottomFeedbackContent\" role=\"group\"><span class=\"bottomFeedbackText\" id=\"bottomFeedbackText\">Was this topic helpful?</span><div class=\"bottomFeedbackButtonGroup\"><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2527047\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-up\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-up\"></use></svg><span>Like</span></a><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2527047\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-down\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-down\"></use></svg><span>Dislike</span></a></div></div></div><div style=\"position: fixed; bottom: 170px; right: 70px; cursor: pointer; transition-duration: 0.2s; transition-timing-function: linear; transition-delay: 0s; z-index: 3; opacity: 0; visibility: hidden; transition-property: opacity, visibility;\"><button aria-label=\"Scroll to top\" class=\"zDocsScrollTopBtn\" data-tooltip-content=\"Scroll to top\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsBackToTopToolTip\" id=\"zDocsScrollToTop\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-next\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-next\"></use></svg></button></div></body></html>", "text": "Defining Popup Forms Add to My Topics Add selected topic and subtopics Add Topic & Subtopics with topic head Add entire publication Watch Download PDF Save selected topic Save selected topic and subtopics Save entire publication Share Email Link Copy Link Feedback Last Updated Sept 12, 2024 Summarize Uniface 10.4 Defining Popup Forms Use the Window Type and other component instance properties to define a popup form. For more information, see Window Type (WindowType) and Popup Window . To define a popup form, set the Window Type property to Popup . You can do this in the Window Properties of the form, or in ProcScript when creating the component instance. For example, a form with the following code defines a popup form in the default position. (The Background Color of the popup form is Info .) trigger detail; of FLD1 newinstance \"POPUP_FRM\", \"popup\", \"windowtype=popup\" activate \"popup\" end Copy By default, the popup form is positioned below the FLD1 field, starting from the bottom left corner. To change the position of the popup form, set the Position window property. This can only be done in ProcScript. For example, the following code changes the anchor point for the popup window to the bottom right corner, and displays to below and to the left of that corner: trigger detail; of FLD1 newinstance \"POPUP_FRM\", \"popup\", \"windowtype=popup ; position=BOTTOMRIGHT_DOWNLEFT\" activate \"popup\" end Copy Optionally, set other properties of the popup window using the Properties Inspector or the newinstance ProcScript statement. In the Properties Inspector, click the More icon ( ) of the component's Window Properties to open the window properties dialog. In ProcScript when creating the component instance. In this example, POPUP_NORMAL is a normal form with the Caption and Close properties set to true . When displayed as a popup form, these properties are ignored by default. However, they are applied when InheritWinProps is true . trigger detail; of FLD1 newinstance \"POPUP_NORMAL\", \"popup\", \"windowtype=popup ; InheritWinProps=true ; position=BOTTOMRIGHT_UPRIGHT\" activate \"popup\" end Copy For more information, see InheritWinProps and Auto Close (AutoClose) . To refine the position of the popup form, so that it can be displayed from a specific point inside or outside the widget. set the PopupRect widget property. This can only be done in ProcScript using the $fieldproperties function. For example, the following code defines a rectangle of 100 by 10 pixels, starting 4 characters to the right and 1 character down from the upper left corner of the field. trigger detail; of FLD1 newinstance \"POPUP_FRM\", \"popup\", \"windowtype=popup\" $fieldproperties(FLD1) = \"popuprect=4,1,100px,10px\" activate \"popup\" end Copy Related Links Popup Forms Popup forms are displayed as secondary windows that are anchored to a field, although their position is completely configurable. They can be used in situations where you want to display or gather a limited amount of data, for example, in a ribbon bar or super tooltip. Was this topic helpful? Like Dislike"}